# tiny.tt: short link redirects for Tiny Tapeout
#
# Standard Cloudflare Pages / Netlify _redirects format:
#   <source>  <destination>  [status]
#
# Status defaults to 302 if omitted. Use 301 for permanent.
# Lines starting with `#` are comments; blank lines are ignored.
#
# Add a link by editing this file and opening a PR.
#
# Reserved paths (cannot be used as slugs):
#   /_dashboard, /_dashboard/api/stats, /robots.txt, /favicon.ico
#
# The `/*` catchall at the bottom is required: it handles the bare domain
# (tiny.tt/) and any unknown slug.

/gh        https://github.com/TinyTapeout     302

/*         https://tinytapeout.com/           302
